    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cornflour </strong>and <strong>reserved pineapple juice </strong>to a pot with your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>brown sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min over a medium heat or until the sauce begins to thicken to a syrup-like consistency – this is your <strong>teriyaki sauce</strong></p>",
