    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut a slit into the top of each<strong> hot dog bun</strong></p><p>Once the sausage[s] have had 25 min, add the <strong>cut</strong> <strong>hot dog bun[s]</strong> to the other side of the tray and return the tray to the oven for 2-3 min or until the hot dog buns are warmed through</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p>",
